        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Real testing, not theoretical comparison</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">A consultant built her business website on Wix. Needed: booking system, client portal, payment processing, blog. Wix App Marketplace had everything she needed. Perfect, right?</p>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Problems emerged:</strong> Wix loads ALL apps on every page. 12 apps = 12 scripts loading = PageSpeed score of 48. Site took 6 seconds to load. Mobile visitors bounced before page finished loading.</p>

          <div class="bg-indigo-100 border-l-[4px] border-indigo-500 p-4 my-4">
