          </div>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>The switch to Webflow:</strong> Rebuilt site without apps. Built booking system with Webflow CMS. Built client portal using memberstack. Built custom payment integration. All clean, fast, professional code. PageSpeed score: 94. Site loads in 1.1 seconds.</p>

