        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is Webflow or Wix better for website building?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Webflow wins overall (8.5/10 vs 8.2/10) with superior design quality (9.0/10 vs 8.0/10), better flexibility (9.5/10 vs 7.5/10), powerful CMS (9.5/10), and code export. Wix offers better ease of use (8.5/10 vs 7.0/10), massive app marketplace (5000+ apps), and more affordable pricing ($10 vs $15/month). Webflow is better for designers and agencies. Wix is better for beginners and users needing specific app features.</p>
        </div>

