        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Which loads faster for visitors?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Webflow typically loads faster. Webflow sites achieve 85-95 PageSpeed scores with clean code. Wix sites often score 60-80 because apps load extra JavaScript on every page. Each Wix app adds scripts that slow loading‚Äî5 apps can mean 3-4 seconds longer load time. Webflow builds features natively without app bloat. If performance matters for SEO and user experience, Webflow wins.</p>
        </div>

